Sackboy is back, this time with playable new friends in an all new handcrafted
adventure. In LittleBigPlanet 3, Sackboy is transported to a new planet called
Bunkum, a creative paradise where abundant ideas drift through the sky.
Unwittingly, Sackboy helps release three mythical creatures called the Titans
who aim to ruin Bunkum and transform the world s most unskilled Creator,
Newton, into a terrible monster.
To restore balance to the land, Sackboy is going to need help in the form of
Bunkum's ancient heroes: Toggle, OddSock and Swoop
